data.description: Looking for a newer property with character and uniqeness? This prestigious Kyle carter built propety features 3 beds, 2 baths, an office, a 3 car garage & indoor laundry hookups! Located in the beautiful san lauren olive dr area, you wont want to miss the wide open split wing floor plan this home has to offer! With amazing landscaping & a swimming pool with a waterfall cascade this home is ready for those hot summer days! 26 Paid off solar panels will help keep energy costs low. Call your preffered realtor and schedule your private showing today.
